           <div class="content">
            <h1>Minister of Transport and Communications</h1>
            <h2>Magnhild Meltveit Kleppa</h2>
            
                    <a href="/en/dep/sd/about-the-ministry/magnhild-meltveit-kleppa/Speeches-and-articles.html?id=582612">Minister of Transport and Communications Magnhild Meltveit Kleppa - Speeches and articles</a>
                
